<template>
    <v-main>
        <v-container>
            <v-text-field class="rounded" :loading="isLoading" label="Szukaj..." append-inner-icon="mdi-magnify"></v-text-field>
            <!-- TODO funkcja loading przy zapytaniu -->
            <v-row>
                <v-col v-for="n in 1" :key="n">
                    <ShopCard v-for="x in numberOfCards" :onlyYourContent="seller" :key="x" cardName="" imageSrc=""
                        userAvatar="" userName="" cardDesc="" />
                </v-col>
            </v-row>
        </v-container>
    </v-main>
</template>

<script>
import '@mdi/font/css/materialdesignicons.css'
import ShopCard from '@/components/ShopCard.vue'

export default {
    name: 'NavBar',
    components: {
        ShopCard
    },
    data() {
        return {
            isLoading: false
        }
    },
    props: {
        numberOfCards: {
            type: String,
            require: true
        },
        seller: {
            type: Boolean,
            require: true
        }
    }
    }
</script>
